rComments: Super kind and caring proff. wants his students to succeed, gives really clear feedback, and is very encouraging.  The class had a lot of discussion periods, but he does not get mad or frustrated if people are not speaking, he just fills in the gaps himself.  no midterm, just 3 assignments with very clear and manageable criteria. absolutely loved

such a kind-hearted professor who genuinely cares for his students. He's thorough, clear, and always willing to help you if you're struggling. I always felt comfortable and heard during his class. Also super accommodating and just wants the best for his students.

Prof Williams was the best teacher I've had yet. He was so considerate of midterms and exams that he pushed back the due dates for all our assignments. He never forced us to speak on zoom, and was very kind in how he answered our questions. There wasn't a midterm, only 3 assignments which he explains thoroughly! Also responded to emails very fast!

My fav prof! He was so helpful. Made the readings and stories bearable to read. His lectures were short and to the point. His feedback was always helpful. He is accessible through email constantly. Overall he is a wonderful prof!
